To run this example, you will need to follow the instructions given
when interactively loading the AlphaFold module on how to agree to
the license to obtain the parameters file.
This requires registering at https://forms.gle/svvpY4u2jsHEwWYS6 and
agreeing to Google's terms of use. Once you have obtained your copy
of the parameters, place the file in a "models" folder in your working folder.

This parameters file can then be used for any of your subsequent
runs of AlphaFold 3.

